9. Bxf6 { That's the right move, we have to force the exchange of the queens. }
9... Bxd1 10. Bxd8 Rxd8
{ Black has to take on d8, if he doesn't, he will be down in material. } 11. c3
{ This is the best move. After  11.Rxd1  Nxc2  we would give Black better chances. }
11... Be2 { The only way to play for equality. } 12. cxd4 Bxc4 13. Rc1
{ Black will have problems on the c-file. } 13... Be6
{ This natural move will promise us some activity. } 14. d5
{ Gaining space a tempo. } 14... Bd7 15. Rxc7 *

